  "2388680": {
    "name": "Monospaced Lovers: Prologue",
    "steam_appid": 2388680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/65f24c9ee237f4748c1adc2954b672ec.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/65f24c9ee237f4748c1adc2954b672ec.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/65f24c9ee237f4748c1adc2954b672ec.mp4?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>穿越一片审视内心、充满幻想的土地，在世界崩溃之前，解开手机上的加密内容。<br><br><strong>《Monospaced Lovers：序章》</strong>是《Monospaced Lovers》的2.0版demo，游戏时长约为<strong>1.5小时</strong>，并且自带可解锁的steam成就。如果你很期待完整版的游戏，请一定要加入愿望单！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/5fe6d19c2812a62a3dc97271bda4e282.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=430 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/5fe6d19c2812a62a3dc97271bda4e282.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >等待探索的手绘世界</h2>✨ 和当地的狸猫聊天，学习如何翻译史莱姆语，探索你朴实家乡的每个角落，找全<strong> 60 件收藏品</strong>。非线性叙事，探索收集类的玩法与 RPG 式的剧情任务相结合，成为游戏的一大特色。<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/04982dde3731e2167a76661009dc4cea.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/04982dde3731e2167a76661009dc4cea.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/04982dde3731e2167a76661009dc4cea.mp4?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹幕与平台游戏的结合</h2>✨ 躲避子弹！游戏具有 4 场以上的弹幕头目战，以及更多的挑战房间，你必须学会以全新的方式进行平台游戏。<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/86fd99e9680e606050337c28ab779ee0.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/86fd99e9680e606050337c28ab779ee0.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/86fd99e9680e606050337c28ab779ee0.mp4?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情逆转和突破类型的展开</h2>✨ 体验<strong>字数10w+</strong>的动人故事。搞笑！刺激！社恐！或许还有哲学？我们放弃了“沉默的主角”这一套路，创造了具有自己的个性和情感的女主角——而且她总是比你快一步。<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/6571eeb175d89c0e2dc4310857b4f769.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/6571eeb175d89c0e2dc4310857b4f769.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/6571eeb175d89c0e2dc4310857b4f769.mp4?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >惊奇和冒险的感觉</h2>✨ 解开棘手的谜题。游戏里的谜题难度令人咂舌，保证让你会忍不住查看提示。这款游戏把玩家当作成人看待，却又能在你有所发现时重新点燃童心——灵感来自《菲斯》、《穆拉纳秘宝》、《姆吉拉的假面》等等。<br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/cbee6e4c86496e3fe4817a403ab71da6.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/cbee6e4c86496e3fe4817a403ab71da6.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/cbee6e4c86496e3fe4817a403ab71da6.mp4?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/16cd7ddb862f5168e67729220e60b33a.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=430 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/16cd7ddb862f5168e67729220e60b33a.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>克拉拉醒来后，发现身边有部不属于自己的手机。<br><br>她在手机上发现了一条令人困惑的信息，是一个名叫“②琎淛と鉮”的黑客留下的，说她留在这个世界上的时间不多了。她唯一的线索是设备上未解锁的一系列加密信息——以及一个神秘的新朋友，他醒来后也发现了一部不属于自己的手机。<br><br>这个神秘的黑客想要什么？他为什么大谈世界末日？而克拉拉在港湾高地朴实而平静的生活，又与这一切有什么关系呢？<br><br>我们只知道，如果她不着手进行这次探索……她的朋友们无论如何也会把她拖进去。<br><br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/0667025ed6325f258b57631afc05fe83.webp?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=3 /></span><br><br>你准备好解开“②琎淛と鉮”之谜，揭开这个陌生而舒适的世界的真相了吗？<br><br>嗯……这并不重要，对不对？<br><br>无论你是否准备好，都无法逃避真相。<br><br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/0f1e8dd6f0e6552cb164e83b7d0ba06d.poster.avif?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/0f1e8dd6f0e6552cb164e83b7d0ba06d.webm?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/0f1e8dd6f0e6552cb164e83b7d0ba06d.mp4?t=1698774877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>​<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388680/extras/0667025ed6325f258b57631afc05fe83.webp?t=1698774877\" width=612 height=3 /></span><br><br><strong>如果你期待完整版，请将《Monospaced Lovers》加入愿望单！</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作团队</h2><strong>代码与剧情</strong>：Stefan Bhagwandin (@_eternal)<br><strong>美术</strong>：Dannica Doplayna (@sphenop_s)<br><strong>音乐</strong>：Michi (@ChillMichi)<br><strong>视觉特效动画</strong>：Weilin Zhang (@xenophoss)<br><strong>声音设计</strong>：Stefan Moser (@effoharkay)<br><br><strong>西班牙语本地化</strong>: Diego Almada Osuna (@Dunkelheyt)<br><strong>俄语本地化</strong>: Stepan Spichak (Aesthetic Dialectic @adtl48)<br><strong>简体中文本地化</strong>: Kakihara MasO (@KakiharaM)<br><strong>日语本地化</strong>: Toshiya Namba (@lonechallenger)<br><strong>土耳其语本地化</strong>: Plus Localization (Website)",
